para_trans: Sub-Divisional Water Conservation Officer Group-A (Construction) and other similar posts in respect of transfer of officers of this cadre.
Department of Soil and Water Conservation,
Government Order No: Establishment-2025 / E-1386894 / Jal-2

Regulation of transfers of Government of Maharashtra employees B. In accordance with the provisions of the Prohibition of Delays in the discharge of Government Duties Act, 2005, 4 (4) and 4 (5), the following officers are being posted on special transfers, on administrative grounds, with the approval of the competent authority B. Subsequent superior authorities:

The aforesaid ARMA mentioned officers shall take charge of the new post forthwith and submit their report of assumption of office to the Government without delay. Also, since they are being transferred as per their request, they will not be paid the tenure of office and the incidental allowance.
This Government Order is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
